= Modules

Modules extend the core functionality of Remarkd with additional features and capabilities.

== Overview

Modules provide extended functionality beyond the core parser features. They can be registered with the Remarkd instance to add new capabilities.

== Module Types

This category includes the following modules:

* *Include Module* - Include content from other files

== Usage

Modules must be registered with the Remarkd instance before use. Click on any feature above to see examples and learn how to use modules in your documents.


